Good.
Bring everything you've got.

37:32.198 --> 37:36.370
This way, Dr. Love.
Dr. Love! This way!

37:37.989 --> 37:39.285
What's going on?

37:40.614 --> 37:42.489
Just watch your sisters.
We'll be back.

37:50.240 --> 37:52.660
Get the tarp up.
I don't want her getting wet.

37:53.656 --> 37:55.202
- Get her up.
- Okay.

37:55.365 --> 38:00.116
Help me. One, two, three...
Take it easy.

38:00.323 --> 38:01.369
- Gloves?
- Gone.

38:01.447 --> 38:03.413
- Betadine?
- Also gone.

38:03.781 --> 38:06.657
I knew I brought that whiskey
for something.

38:10.948 --> 38:13.119
- Farber, get the line in.
- Can you hold that for me?

38:13.198 --> 38:14.948
- Gloves?
- Everything gone.

38:15.240 --> 38:17.581
Here, can you hold that for me?
Thank you.

38:23.073 --> 38:25.244
Take the whiskey.

38:29.698 --> 38:31.040
What's wrong, Mommy?

38:34.531 --> 38:35.782
