01:07:27.488 --> 01:07:30.364
So, I get groceries.

01:07:30.654 --> 01:07:32.780
I make us dinner.

01:07:40.196 --> 01:07:41.572
I'm not hungry-

01:07:45.737 --> 01:07:47.204
It doesn't matter.

01:07:47.987 --> 01:07:49.658
I make us dinner,

01:07:50.321 --> 01:07:52.321
and you eat with me.

01:08:18.029 --> 01:08:19.654
Too dark in here.

01:08:24.696 --> 01:08:26.117
Ay yi yi!

01:08:30.196 --> 01:08:31.787
Ah, c'est...

01:08:34.862 --> 01:08:37.283
Three days of depressions
too many.

01:08:37.571 --> 01:08:38.571
<i>Eat.</i>

01:08:41.029 --> 01:08:42.371
I will...

01:08:50.779 --> 01:08:52.620
Sarie... leave them... really.“

01:08:53.737 --> 01:08:55.113
I leave...

