in one minute.

01:08:59.569 --> 01:09:01.821
You don't have to do <i>that...</i>

01:09:04.946 --> 01:09:07.037
Just a second!
Don't say "thank you,"

01:09:07.113 --> 01:09:10.578
Just a second, I'll get Sarie.
Excuse me!

01:09:10.696 --> 01:09:11.696
Sarie!

01:09:17.821 --> 01:09:19.197
<i>He's here...</i>

01:09:44.279 --> 01:09:45.823
I'm very sorry Miss Peterson,

01:09:45.904 --> 01:09:48.451
I asked him to wait.

01:09:48.904 --> 01:09:50.575
Please, Mister,
please come back down.

01:09:50.654 --> 01:09:51.529
This is not right.

01:09:51.612 --> 01:09:53.238
It's okay, Oom.

01:09:54.238 --> 01:09:55.954
It's okay.

01:10:07.862 --> 01:10:09.329
Go!

01:10:26.029 --> 01:10:29.825
I'll just leave this here.

01:10:36.570 --> 01:10:38.287
Come over here.

01:10:47.904 --> 01:10:49.449
Closer.

01:10:55.445 --> 01:10:58.117
Wren, that couldn't be
the last time

